OL,3,CJersey Bulls legend announces
OL,4,Cretirement
OL,6,FVeteran Jersey Bulls defender Luke
OL,7,FCampbell has announced his retirement.
OL,9,FThe 37-year-old has been a key player
OL,10,Fsince the club's founding in 2019 and
OL,11,Fhas made 201 appearances.
OL,13,FHe scored 45 goals during his seven-
OL,14,Fyear spell and helped the Bulls to two
OL,15,Fpromotion-winning seasons.
OL,17,FCampbell's final appearance ended in
OL,18,Fheartbreak after the Bulls lost to AFC
OL,19,FWhyteleafe on penalties in the
OL,20,FIsthmian League South East play-off
OL,21,Fsemi-finals.
