OL,3,CJersey Bulls legend announces
OL,4,Cretirement
OL,6,FIn a social media post, the club
OL,7,Fthanked Campbell for his services and
OL,8,Fcalled him a "club stalwart".
OL,10,F"Luke has served the club with dignity
OL,11,Fand class throughout his 7-year
OL,12,Fspell," the club stated.
OL,14,F"The Silver Fox has given the club
OL,15,Fcountless memorable moments that will
OL,16,Flive long in the memory."
